  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 11-46-9, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO PROVIDE AN EXCEPTION FROM IMMUNITY FOR ANY CIVIL CLAIM AGAINST AN EMPLOYEE OF A GOVERNMENTAL ENTITY ARISING OUT OF ANY ACT OR OMISSION RELATING TO POLICE PROTECTION WHERE VIOLATIONS OF STATE CONSTITUTIONAL RIGHTS ARE ALLEGED AGAINST THE EMPLOYEE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
